8-09-08T04:43:04.000Z","msg":"係香港人先講埋呢啲鳩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老板人生只係為左打工咩<br />\n打工咪為搵食同理想<br />\n<br />\n我寧願佢可以用佢既信念 終身奉獻佢既社會倡議同抗爭事業<br />\n起呢個環境下更需要呢啲人<br />\n只要相信自己係岩 就去試下做<br />\n唔work 就換下方式做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33179f23c796a3b23b7c8bfa505830b8c12a5e04","tid":810474,"uid":53421,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:54:58.000Z","msg":"佢點都好過熱狗班撚屌既<br />\n果d咩射撚滿"},{"pid":"18ffccdd94ccd0da0ac43fdf27f866f10e92688f","tid":810474,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ce44a488d24dc4bdfd288261d22fcabeed98528","tid":810474,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"702ffb8666d008d69a51e1b7463b9b4aedf6cd98","tid":810474,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:27:06.000Z","msg":"長毛被人dq左之後，社民連成班人靠咩為生？？老土d講句，依個時勢搞社運係死路一條，趁後生搵份工好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"佢而家重有咩工請？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:55:48.000Z","msg":"陶君行都做緊會計啦，黃浩銘好似碩士黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d013f0a0d91d606c9a7fadae87d135799e4f30","tid":810474,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:56:47.000Z","msg":"村民唔係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60b470e6685a0ba359f88702279fb7ad3b3b347","tid":810474,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0a74361d6b29b2252df234203a018b52e65b8f5b","tid":810474,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"第一張果個係黃浩銘？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:02:52.000Z","msg":"肥咗好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}